sentences.english: The shipping charges for returning samples will be added to your final invoice.
sentences.chinese: 運費爲返回的樣品將增加來您最後的發貨票。

sentences.english: Invoiced packaging on loan will not be paid for; it will be returned carriage paid.
sentences.chinese: 包裝費不單獨支付，而是與運費一起支付。

sentences.english: Shipping I will let you know when we get exact amount.
sentences.chinese: 海運費的話，等我們知道具體金額再告訴你。

sentences.english: The price does not include shipping and handling.
sentences.chinese: 此價格不包含運費和處理費。

sentences.english: Freight prepaid to Buenos aires in transit to Asuncion Paraguay.
sentences.chinese: 運費付至布宜諾斯艾利斯，再轉運到巴拉圭的亞松森。

sentences.english: But the plan means forgoing storage revenue and standard handling fees.
sentences.chinese: 但此計劃意味着放棄倉儲的收入和標準搬運費。

sentences.english: But I think Such shirts packed in cardboard cartons can save freight cost.
sentences.chinese: 但是我認爲使用硬紙箱包裝這批襯衣可以節省運費。

sentences.english: Ocean freight rates started 2009 with a positive tone.
sentences.chinese: 2009年起海洋運費呈現積極態勢。

sentences.english: We have been able to transship cargoes at Hong Kong.
sentences.chinese: 貨物如果轉運，我們得多付運費。

sentences.english: The shipping company, for additional freight, undertakes to make all arrangements to get the goods to their destination.
sentences.chinese: 海運公司將承擔額外的運費負責將貨物運達目的地。

sentences.english: I will return this shipment and the freight 6 cost will be born by you.
sentences.chinese: 我會將這批貨寄回，運費由你們支付。

sentences.english: If be inside affirmatory time nondelivery, consumer will win compensation of entire fund transportation expenses.
sentences.chinese: 如在承諾時間內沒有送達，消費者將獲全款運費賠償。

sentences.english: Will you accept the ocean freight price ?
sentences.chinese: 不知道你對海運費的價格是否接受？

sentences.english: Do we charge for shipping and handling?
sentences.chinese: 我們要收取運費和處理費嗎？

sentences.english: The seller must pay the costs and freight neceary to bring the goods to the named port of destination.
sentences.chinese: 即賣方必須支付貨物運至目的港所需要的運費和費用。

sentences.english: Please clear the goods and forward them by rail to our address, carriage pay.
sentences.chinese: 請將該貨物報關後，通過鐵路交本公司，運費已付。

definition: to place an order/to order/an order (of goods)
